text: Iaz may refer to several places in Romania: * Iaz, a village in Strugari Commune, Bacău County * Iaz, a village in Obreja Commune, Caraș-Severin County * Iaz, a village in Plopiș Commune, Sălaj County * Iaz, a village in Dornești Commune, Suceava County * Iaz, a village in Solești Commune, Vaslui County * Iaz (Barcău), a tributary of the Barcău in Sălaj County * Iaz, another name for the river Mândra in Brașov County * Iaz, a tributary of the Șușița in Gorj County
title: Iaz
